e=2010-11-17 |archive-date=2011-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007163138/http://www.prixarcdetriomphe.com/admin/presse/QatarPrixArcdeTriomphe_EN.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[莫雅|莫雅]]已經連續兩年在此賽事成功奪冠<ref name="2010IJC">{{cite web |url=http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/r-moore-hong-kong-moore-bags-jockeys-championship/797359/international/# |title=Moore wins International Jockeys' Championship |publisher=Racing Post |language= |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2011-11-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/63FgLyaAf?url=http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/r-moore-hong-kong-moore-bags-jockeys-championship/797359/international/ |archivedate=2011-11-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[莫狄|莫狄]]即使在今年沒有巴利多爾馬房支持，但仍成為愛爾蘭冠軍騎師<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|authorlink=Marty McGee|coauthors=|title=Murtagh claims fifth Irish Flat jockeys' crown|url=http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=943538|work=|publisher=[[Racing_Post|Racing Post]]|date=2011-11-06|accessdate=2011-11-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120906233530/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=943538|archivedate=2012-09-06}}</ref>。[[福永祐一|福永祐一]]雖然今年未在日本大賽取佔優，但在騎師榜佔據前列<ref>{{cite web |url=http://jra.jp/news/201111/111702.html |script-title=ja:福永　祐一騎手が香港騎手招待レースに出場 |publisher=日本中央競馬會 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629064848/http://jra.jp/news/201111/111702.html |archivedate=2012-06-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在紐西蘭，冒起的新星[[麥道朗|麥道朗]]成為以破紀錄的姿態成為2010-11年度冠軍騎師，這次是他首次到香港客串<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.turfclub.com.sg/DesktopModules/AdvancedArticles/ArticleDetail.aspx?ItemId=8190&ModuleId=1138&TabId=85&PortalId=0 |title=McDonald to ride at Derby weekend |publisher=新加坡賽馬公會 |accessdate=2010-11-17 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。此外十一屆冠軍騎師[[韋達_(賽馬)|韋達]]自動以香港代表身份獲得參賽資格。本屆賽事總共有四名騎師首次參與<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink=Marty McGee |coauthors= |title=國泰航空香港國際賽事：五將首次入選騎師賽 |url=http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_mai