在第一關，戴圖理的旅遊小子在直路帶出，順利以兩個馬位勝出賽事。接著在第二關，麥道朗憑新力飛在直路如箭般殺上，反勝浦東之威奪冠，麥道朗曾經一度在積分榜領先。在第三關，李慕華的玉峽生輝出奇不異地在直路帶出，爆出半冷。在第三關後，麥道朗、戴圖理、李慕華及薜達祺仍有機會奪冠。來到最後一關，戴圖理的帝豪名駒，一口氣在直路由居中超越其他對手反勝，反觀李慕華的明興寶寶只得第11。戴圖理第三度奪得國際騎師賽冠軍，今次是戴圖理首次代表意大利勝出賽事，奪冠次數與韋達併頭<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2011-12/news_2011120702327.html |title= 國泰航空國際騎師錦標賽 戴圖理勝出兩關勇奪冠軍 |publisher= 香港賽馬會 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |archive-date= 2014-01-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140122180655/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2011-12%2Fnews_2011120702327.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first= Lewis |last= Porteous |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= Frankie Dettori lands third jockeys' challenge |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/happy-valley-hong-kong-frankie-dettori-wins-third-jockeys-challenge/958771/international/ |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2011-12-08 |accessdate= 2011-12-09 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120908053542/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/happy-valley-hong-kong-frankie-dettori-wins-third-jockeys-challenge/958771/international/ |archivedate= 2012-09-08 }}</ref>。

