險勝墨爾本盃<ref name="melbournecup"/>，之後由指定騎師韋紀力策騎。[[火龍駒|火龍駒]]為應屆香港冠軍暨遮打盃得主<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2011-05/news_2011052901917.html |title= 「火龍駒」奪取渣打冠軍暨遮打盃 |publisher= 香港賽馬會 |date= 2011-05-29 |accessdate= 2011-12-01 |archive-date= 2020-07-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200703053458/https://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2011-05%2Fnews_2011052901917.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>，後來征戰澳洲兩度取得獎金。自由好在中距離復甦，勝出二級賽[[馬會盃|馬會盃]]<ref name="JCcup">{{cite news |first= Jeremy |last= Greene |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Thumbs Up set for Vase date after dramatic win |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=950521&argument=700328 |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2011-11-16 |accessdate= 2011-11-28 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20130427181538/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=950521&argument=700328 |archivedate= 2013-04-27 }}</ref>，更在賽事專攻香港瓶<ref name="CXHKIRSUPPLY"/>。紅杉木在2010年香港瓶跑獲亞軍後，之後兩度在賽事取得亞軍，以後補身加入。[[好先生|好先生]]2010年在香港冠軍暨遮打盃勝出。紅色禮物在6月攻下卻拉盃後<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Red Cadeaux thrashes Curragh Cup rivals |url= http://www.irishracing.com/v5newsitem?prt=L&prid=54240 |work=  |publisher= Irish Racing |date= 2010-06-25 |accessdate= 2011-11-29 |archive-date= 2019-08-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190822101006/https://www.irishracing.com/news?prt=L&prid=54240 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，接著在墨爾本盃跑獲亞軍<ref name="melbournecup"/>。極品絲綢雖然久未有頭馬進帳，但最近兩戰均獲得獎金，從而以後補身份參賽。犀利靈原為不注目雌馬，但在10月舉行的[[加拿大國際錦標|加拿大國際錦標]]一鳴驚人，擊敗眾多雄馬奪冠而回<ref>{{cite news |first= Jack |last= Shinar |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Filly Sarah Lynx Wins Canadian International |url= http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/65595/filly-sarah-lynx-wins-canadian-international |publisher= bloodhorse.com |date= 2011-10-16 |accessdate= 2011-11-30 |archive-date= 2014-10-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141023023602/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/65595/filly-sarah-lynx-wins-canadian-international |dead-url= no }}</ref>。威達馬在無緣凱旋門大賽後，順利攻下二級賽[[巴黎市議會大賽|巴黎市議會大賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Francesso |last= Rossi |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Vadamar makes all for Group 2 success |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=932994&argument=766356 |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2011-10-16 |accessdate= 2011-12-01 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120908193815/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=932994&argument=766356 |archivedate= 2012-09-08 }}</ref>，同樣以補充報名加入<ref name="CXHKIRSUPPLY">{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2011-11/news_2011112301525.html |title=二○一一年國泰航空香港國際賽事 - 補充報名馬匹名單 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |accessdate=2010-11-25 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618125808/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2011-11%2Fnews_2011112301525.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

