都市風光並非歐洲頂級賽駒，但表現稍定，10月在法國三級賽帕斯錦標取勝<ref>{{cite news |first= James |last= Burn |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Cityscape scores cosy Group 3 win for Charlton |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=939999&argument=713852 |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2011-10-30 |accessdate= 2011-12-05 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120908205939/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=939999&argument=713852 |archivedate= 2012-09-08 }}</ref>。占美大亨是紐西蘭馬王<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Racing: Jimmy Choux takes Horse of Year title at a canter |url= http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=10747767 |work=  |publisher= [[新西蘭先驅報|新西蘭先驅報]] |date= 2010-08-27 |accessdate= 2011-11-30 |archive-date= 2014-01-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140112080407/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/sport/news/article.cfm?c_id=4&objectid=10747767 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，2010年至賽前在澳紐均取得好表現，在角逐[[覺士盾|覺士盾]]前勝出一場一級賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2011-12/news_2011120101630.html |title=「占美大亨」強勢進襲香港一哩錦標 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |accessdate=2011-12-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305202647/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2011-12%2Fnews_2011120101630.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。上屆殿軍的驪勝名駒在凱旋門大賽賽期勝出[[韋士登錦標|韋士登錦標]]。上屆冠軍締造美麗除勝出2010年香港一哩錦標<ref name="HKmile">{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 巫斯義締造美麗 首位贏過國際賽四項錦標 |url= http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20101213&sec_id=3403908&art_id=14759350 |work=  |publisher= 蘋果日報 |date= 2010-12-13 |accessdate= 2011-12-01 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115923/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20101213&sec_id=3403908&art_id=14759350 |dead-url= no }}</ref>外還勝出[[董事盃_(香港)|董事盃]]以及[[女皇銀禧紀念盃|女皇銀禧紀念盃]]<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 賽後新聞：締造美麗G1三連勝 |url= http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110307&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15046470 |work=  |publisher= 蘋果日報 |date= 2011-03-07 |accessdate= 2011-12-03 |archive-date= 2019-02-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190214080717/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110307&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15046470 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。去年在國際賽日出戰一班賽的軍事攻略攻下了冠軍一哩賽<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 大摩包辦三寶 　軍事攻略奪冠軍一哩 |url= http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110426&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15199273 |work=  |publisher= 蘋果日報 |date= 2011-04-26 |accessdate= 2011-12-03 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304190552/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110426&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15199273 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。步步穩曾勝出兩屆冠軍一哩賽，惟欠下香港一哩錦標。勁飛寶在首戰分級賽中，成功越級挑戰勝出[[主席錦標|主席錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 賽後新聞：跳兩班蝕21分照贏G2 勁飛寶月底撼外隊 |url= http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110404&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15134111 |work=  |publisher= 蘋果日報 |date= 2010-04-04 |accessdate= 2011-12-01 |archive-date= 2019-02-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190214080717/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20110404&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15134111 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。卡達聖在馬會一哩錦標擊敗馬王雄心威龍<ref name="JCmile">{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 馬王大讓賽全程四叠雄心威龍輸條線 |url= http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20111121&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15818345 |work=  |publisher= 蘋果日報 |date= 2011-11-20 |accessdate= 2011-12-02 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202049/http://hk.racing.nextmedia.com/art_main.php?showdate=20111121&sec_id=3403908&art_id=15818345 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。君子一言在角逐2010年香港打吡前是一匹不敗賽駒，之後因傷患影響表現反覆。川河勁駒勝出精英盃，過往在二班也曾勝出1600米。杜拜之金在三歲時勝出[[慶典一哩錦標|慶典一哩錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Tom |last= Kerr |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Brilliant Hughes steers Dubawi Gold to victory |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=906054&argument=759530 |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2010-08-27 |accessdate= 2011-12-02 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120907000211/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=906054&argument=759530 |archivedate= 2012-09-07 }}</ref>。人人興旺雖然未跑過這樣頂級的賽事，但是在一哩或以下路程的表現相當穩定，對上一次勝出是5月1日的二班賽。莎貝寶駒在[[太陽戰車錦標|太陽戰車錦標]]連奪三屆冠軍<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Sahpresa to land Sun Chariot hat-trick at Newmarket |url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/horseracing/8785605/Sahpresa-to-land-Sun-Chariot-hat-trick-at-Newmarket.html |work=  |publisher= [[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]] |date= 2011-09-23 |accessdate= 2011-12-05 |archive-date= 2011-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110925095144/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/horseracing/8785605/Sahpresa-to-land-Sun-Chariot-hat-trick-at-Newmarket.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>，此外在與雄馬對陣賽事中也留下不錯的表現。夏威夷鳥是2010年度的日本雌馬三冠，2011年與日本馬王[[迷人景致|迷人景致]]交戰時擊敗對手，在[[維多利亞一哩賽|維多利亞一哩賽]]順利奪冠<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |script-title= ja:【ヴィクトリアＭ】“ウオッカ超え”のレコードＶ |url= http://www.sponichi.co.jp/gamble/news/2011/05/16/kiji/K20110516000828620.html |work=  |publisher= Sport Nippon |date= 2010-05-15 |accessdate= 2011-11-30 |archive-date= 2015-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924182953/http://www.sponichi.co.jp/gamble/news/2011/05/16/kiji/K20110516000828620.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。後備補上的戶外名駒，在香港四歲馬賽事留下不錯的表現，在今季亦取得一場勝利。

