香港馬王雄心威龍是賽事的大熱門。起步後雄心威龍一如以往留後跑，加州萬里反而跟前，賽事步速不快，讓滿綵輕鬆帶出，在直路前位置未有太大的改變。轉自直路初段加州萬里一度被困，但在滿綵乏力後讓蔡明紹找到空位，雖然大熱門雄心威龍後上追回不少，但是力盡下反被魔法幻影超越，結果加州萬里勝出<ref name="cup">{{cite news |first= Lewis |last= Pouteous |authorlink=  |coauthors=  |title= California wins HK Cup with Dragon only fourth |url= http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/california-memory-hong-kong-california-wins-cup-with-dragon-fourth/960821/international/ |work=  |publisher= racingpost.com |date= 2011-12-11 |accessdate= 2011-12-12 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20130427205046/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/california-memory-hong-kong-california-wins-cup-with-dragon-fourth/960821/international/ |archivedate= 2013-04-27 }}</ref>，魔法幻影第二，季軍是前衛先鋒，雄心威龍只得第四。

